    Courgette curry

    Visit
    5
    (15)
     1 hr Yield: 4
    Scoop out the seeds before slicing and frying the courgettes to achieve a firmer texture in this ...
    Ingredients
    • 3 medium courgettes
    • 2-3 tbsp sunflower oil
    • 1 red onion, halved and finely sliced
    • 1-2 red chillies (depending on preference), finely chopped
    • 40g ginger, peeled and finely grated

    Irresistible Chicken Curry

    Visit
    5
    (7)
     1 hr, 5 min Yield: Makes 4 servings
    This Indian-inspired chicken curry is rich, creamy and saucy. Serve it with rice (try Coconut Rice) ...
    Ingredients
    • 1 to 1 pounds boneless, skinless chicken thighs or breast
    • 1 1/2 teaspoons fine sea salt
    • 1 teaspoon ground cumin
    • 3/4 teaspoons ground coriander
    • 1/2 teaspoon ground turmeric
